We shot your friend early this morning.

01:20:11.400 --> 01:20:13.300
Why do you bother with such scum?

01:20:15.300 --> 01:20:16.400
Why?

01:20:20.200 --> 01:20:23.399
Look, go to your cabaret

01:20:23.400 --> 01:20:25.400
and entertain the rich.

01:20:36.400 --> 01:20:37.400
Let's go, Fico.

01:20:45.300 --> 01:20:46.200
Go.

01:20:55.300 --> 01:20:57.299
Cha-cha-cha!

01:20:57.300 --> 01:20:58.300
Va.

