Are you okay?

01:36:07.401 --> 01:36:09.400
...family?

01:36:14.300 --> 01:36:17.299
Help! Help!

01:36:17.300 --> 01:36:18.300
Dono, put your head up.

01:36:18.400 --> 01:36:20.399
Put your head up. Put your head.

01:36:20.400 --> 01:36:23.200
Help me! Help!

01:36:27.200 --> 01:36:30.400
Help! Help!

