Hello, Father.

01:36:40.500 --> 01:36:42.400
Hi, son.

01:36:44.400 --> 01:36:50.299
What a great thing to hear.

01:36:50.300 --> 01:36:53.400
No one comes to say hello these days.

01:36:54.300 --> 01:36:56.300
Just good-bye.

01:37:00.400 --> 01:37:01.499
I'm so sorry.

01:37:01.500 --> 01:37:04.399
Yeah, well...

01:37:04.400 --> 01:37:06.300
my brother's resting in peace,

01:37:06.500 --> 01:37:12.200
and Ricardo, unfortunately...

01:37:12.400 --> 01:37:15.399
will have to live with the
consequences of his actions.

01:37:15.400 --> 01:37:20.199
And that's very sad.

01:37:20.200 --> 01:37:23.200
But, uh...

01:37:23.400 --> 01:37:26.300
I would like to talk about you.

01:37:27.200 --> 01:37:28.400
I remember what you said about
the moneylenders in the temple.

01:37:28.500 --> 01:37:30.299
Yeah.

01:37:30.300 --> 01:37:34.199
Well, the self-proclaimed Christ is here,

01:37:34.200 --> 01:37:35.200
and he's all whip.

01:37:35.300 --> 01:37:36.400
I know.

01:37:37.200 --> 01:37:39.400
Federico.

01:37:41.400 --> 01:37:43.200
Yeah.

01:37:43.400 --> 01:37:48.499
Your mother and I...
are worried about you.

01:37:48.500 --> 01:37:51.399
Now we think you should
be leaving the country.

01:37:51.400 --> 01:37:53.299
My place is here with both of you.

01:37:53.300 --> 01:37:54.300
Listen to me.

01:37:54.500 --> 01:37:56.400
No. I'm not gonna leave,

01:37:57.300 --> 01:37:58.200
unless you're gonna come with me.

01:37:58.201 --> 01:38:00.200
Listen to me.

01:38:00.400 --> 01:38:03.399
Listen to me.

01:38:03.400 --> 01:38:08.300
In life, you have to know when to arrive,

01:38:09.200 --> 01:38:11.400
but you have to know when to leave.

01:38:13.400 --> 01:38:16.199
And you should be leaving to a place

01:38:16.200 --> 01:38:19.199
where you can express yourself freely,

01:38:19.200 --> 01:38:21.300
not like here.

01:38:24.300 --> 01:38:26.400
And this will fill our hearts with hope.

01:38:27.300 --> 01:38:31.200
We'll be fine, Fico. We'll be fine.

01:38:40.400 --> 01:38:43.199
I have left you very little, my son.

01:38:43.200 --> 01:38:45.300
How can you say that?

01:38:45.400 --> 01:38:47.299
You've given me the
wealth of your example.

01:38:47.300 --> 01:38:49.300
That's all I need.

